title: SPECTACULAR UPGRADED UNIT IN BRICKELL FLATIRON!
posting_body: ['Spectacular upgraded unit at the iconic Brickell Flatiron.', 'Huge 1 bedroom / 1.5 baths with top of the line Miele appliances, Nest system thermostat, Italian doors, Glass-enclosed shower, Custom made closets & Window treatments, 9-foot ceiling heights, stunning views, premium flooring, among others!', 'Live & play in this luxury building that offers some of the best amenities in the city: Sky club rooftop at the 64th floor offering sky Pool with 360-degree views of Miami and Biscayne Bay, fitness center with the best views of the city, & Wellness Center & Spa.', "Flatiron Club at 18th & 17th floors offering a private movie theater, outdoor lap pool, children's playroom, social lounge room, billiards room, & concierge service.", 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
